{"tid":27417,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女婿唔夠力　輪椅岳母滾墮電梯","createTime":"2016-12-07T10:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T12:13:06.000Z","uid":29836,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4990b5254a2730d91e8ef03484eb8bad6ad15dfc","tid":27417,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJhwaaTIGwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNJhwaaTIGwE&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=0d82c849\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJhwaaTIGwE</a><br />\n【本報訊】沙田偉華商場昨發生扶手電梯意外。中年女婿推着坐輪椅的岳母偕岳丈逛商場，但他們棄用升降機，乘扶手電梯由地下上1樓；女婿疑不夠力跌倒，岳母隨即連人帶輪椅向後翻，兩人同告受傷。<br />\n<br />\n女婿疑半路不夠力<br />\n受傷女婿姓馮（55歲），岳母姓龔（76歲），同行還有姓李岳丈（80歲）。馮穿頭流血，龔婦則頭痛，幸治理後無大礙已經出院。<br />\n現場是偉華商場地下往1樓的扶手電梯，昨晨8時40分，馮偕岳丈岳母到偉華商場逛街，當中龔婦坐輪椅要由馮推動。不過懷疑有人貪方便，他們棄用商場升降機而乘扶手電梯上1樓；但上了8至10級左右，馮疑不夠力向後跌，結果龔婦連輪椅亦一併墮下壓住他。李慌張大叫求救，商場內其他人見狀連忙按停扶手梯，再將兩人及輪椅扶起報警。商場保安員將扶手電梯封鎖暫停使用，通知機電署檢驗。商場升降機距離扶手電梯不過10米，扶手電梯有告示，輪椅、嬰兒車及手推車均不宜使用，市民應注意安全。"},{"pid":"1909fa082813c63997e8c1a13ac7e206e414fbce","tid":27417,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20101209/large/09la9p15n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20101209%2Flarge%2F09la9p15n.jpg&h=b9317baf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c6311e0b2173b10160ce47feb5e4294e5a7d37b","tid":27417,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1079035a9d23db4cdc7b3402ba3e5d598c83636a","tid":27417,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re